This folder (phys516-as06) contains instruction and codes needed to complete assignment 6
for PHYS 516.

as06.pdf: Assignment itself.

Kwon-TBSi-PRB94.pdf: "Transferable tight-binding models for silicon,"
I. Kwon et al., Phys. Rev. B 49, 7242 (1994), from which you obtain tight-binding model
parameters for Si.

ProgrammingTB.pdf: Outline of programming.

tb_util_angstrom.c, tb_util_au.c: C program to set up atomic coordinates in a Si crystal
(either use angstrom or atomic unit of your choice to specify length).

eigen.c: Matrix diagonalization program from Numerical Recipes.
